Class DefaultOwnerGroupIdentifier

  • java.lang.Object

    OwnerGroupIdentifier

    public class DefaultOwnerGroupIdentifier
extends java.lang.Object
implements OwnerGroupIdentifier
    Let's extracting the group name of any given job owner. The name of the extracted name is the first letter of the given owner ID but if none can be found "_" is returned.
